		<description>
#### Package Parameters
The following package parameters can be set:

 * `/analysis[:VSInstanceIds]` - Install SSAS to specified VS2017 instances.
 * `/integration[:VSInstanceIds]` - Install SSIS to specified VS2017 instances.
 * `/reporting[:VSInstanceIds]` - Install SSRS to specified VS2017 instances.

VSInstanceIds is the list of target VS 2017 instance ids seperated by comma. It can be absent when there is only one VS 2017 
instance installed on current machine

To pass parameters, use --params "''" (e.g. choco install ssdt17 [other options] --params="'/analysis /reporting:'").

When no parameters are provided then ONLY the Visual Studio Integrated Shell will be installed.
